            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text addresses the Mesoamerican numerical system. Before proceeding, we suggest studying the following texts:\n- **Yupana (Adition)**: presents how to do sum operation with *Yupana* (<htcite0>).\n- **Overcoming limits**: presents the Mesoamerican vigesimal calendrical system (<htcite1>).\n- **Change of Direction (Part II)**: explains how orders are used in an exclusively vigesimal system (<htcite2>).\n- **Chapter 5 (First Steps):** previous texts from this chapter in the *First Steps* section (<htcite3>).",
               "source": [
