         "id": "SECTION_iupana",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Recalling the *Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay* Method\n\n#### The Quipus\n\nWhen studying the Andean peoples, we observe that in the Andes, quipus were developed that may date back more than four millennia (<htcite0>). These *quipus* (Figure 1), like Mesoamerican numbers, were also written vertically, but they used the decimal base (<htcite1>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "c2ff41fc-7833-4dc2-8882-eaed12a065b7",
                     "text": "Mann, Charles C.",
                     "page": "pp. 1008",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2005",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "6e9bef8c-6ec5-4c04-b583-aea8e6bbec5b",
                     "text": "Quesada, Eugenio de",
                     "page": "",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2016",
                        "month": "",
                        "day": ""
                     }
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgQuipuPanel\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgQuipuPanel', '0%')\" src=\"images/Caral/QuipuPanel.png\" class=\"imgcenter\"/>Figure 1: Panel at the Caral archaeological site, ©ZonaArqueólogicaCaral, (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('720f6dfd-4b86-4e07-a887-1010e1041a4d'); return false;\">Ruta Caral, <htdate0></a> ; <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('03c3743c-d268-4730-ba8e-d36b5c49e781'); return false;\">Youtube - Caral Perú Oficial, <htdate1></a>). Photo taken on <htdate2>, during a visit to the site.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": [
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
                     "year": "2024",
                     "month": "-1",
                     "day": "-1"
                  },
                  {
                     "type": "gregory",
