p\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f2\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f2\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td></tr></tr></table></p><p class=\"desc\">Table 1 – Representation of the movements of the <i>Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay</i> method. CSS inspired by <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillReferenceSource('48dd9187-7ecc-4f54-a387-d9ecc2497de3'); return false;\">W3School</span></a> W3Schools code.</p>",
